        Max / Min
    </h2>
    <p>Use <code>std::min(x,y)</code> or <code>std::max(x,y)</code>
    to find the min or max of two numbers, respectively. 
    </p>
    <pre><code class="lang-cpp">
std::cout << std::max(5,7);
// 7         
    </code></pre>
