        Cmath Header
    </h2>
    <p>
        Include the <code>&lt;cmath&gt;</code> header to gain access to 
        lots of useful math functions. Some examples listed below include the pow function, 
        the sqrt function and the round function. 
    </p>
    <pre><code class="lang-cpp">
#include &lt;cmath&gt;
int main(){
    int x = pow(2,2);
    int y = sqrt(64);
    int z = round(2.89);
    return 0; 
}
    </code></pre>
